鬥力屬最強<br />\n62,63,64軍屬粵系部隊，當中以62軍既戰鬥精神最為頑強、64軍則由軍長和司令官令軍令不一而令戰鬥力太減、63軍則一直想避戰在逃往榆林途中就喪失大半兵力"},{"pid":"2c4ee0cd1b3053bf2113b500164cc44f4937caee","tid":599370,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adc2b7828d2d946cc7ba31c2c4cd817dbf719112","tid":599370,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dd2e989ba1b093f77dff593b3e4725b668b905","tid":599370,"uid":48157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9蛇好波"}]}